谈判，尽早解决边境问题。","newsLink":"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85/20240704-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%96%E9%95%BF%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F%E5%B0%BD%E6%97%A9%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E8%BE%B9%E7%95%8C%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98","thumbnail":"","detailImage":"news/detail/rfi/2024/07/04/1720078456000.webp","sourceId":"rfi"}]